{
  "stem": "21611.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we were 12, and we were at that time smarter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We run away in a different direction.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went on a train and we came to Italy in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a place, they call it Della Samedia, where the [NON-ENGLISH] worked.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We came in the middle of the night, and we got to the place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were on the sidewalks-- we were so tired we were lying on the sidewalks waiting for the daytime to let us in.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they gave us a place in a kibbutz that a rich Jew had a villa, and he gave this for the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At that time, I was very sick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "After the war, I really fell apart.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was very strong in the war, but I fell apart.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was a Jewish professor, his name was Madiano-- he was from Greece.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he took care of the refugees.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he took very good care of me, didn't want me to die.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he was extremely-- he really helped me to survive because I had trouble with my lungs.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I had trouble holding my pregnancy, angiitis.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I had trouble with a breast.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was operated five days of my ninth month.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it didn't even guarantee, not for me, not for the child.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Thank God, I survived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I had a little boy, Michael.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was three years in Italy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The Italian people were the first people who were nice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were so nice to us, to share the piece of bread with us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I could never forget them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "For three years we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And my uncle from Canada, he sent papers through the [NON-ENGLISH]-- they knew where I was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "This was my father's brother.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
